The '''Shu-Wang Prism''' was a [[Crystal/Legends|crystalline]] entrance on [[Solibus IV]]. Opening it led [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Quinlan Vos/Legends|Quinlan Vos]] and his [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] [[Aayla Secura/Legends|Aayla Secura]] to solving the [[Lodi|Mystery of the Lodi]].

